{
  "texts": [
    "Beyond natural language understanding tasks, our study expanded to include experiments on natural language generation tasks.",
    "These experiments were conducted using the GPT-2 medium (355M) and large (774M) models on the E2E NLG Challenge (Novikova et al., 2017).",
    "The pre-trained GPT-2 models were also obtained from the HuggingFace Transformers Library.",
    "To ensure a fair comparison, we reproduced other PEFT methods following the settings defined by Li and Liang (2021a) and Hu et al. (2021).",
    "Please refer to Appendix B.2 for the comprehensive details of our implementation."
  ]
}